<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,1265,1725]" box="[199,1430,1301,1328]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,451,1301,1328]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Original description:</emphasis>
“labbro internamente d’un rosso vivo” [internal part of the lip marked with bright red].
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,1265,1725]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,436,1337,1364]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Material examined:</emphasis>
four glued shells labelled “Dono Bellini” [Donated by Bellini] and “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Sta." authorityName="Sta." class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="subprofuga" subGenus="Heliomanes">
<emphasis box="[1215,1276,1338,1364]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Helix</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[1293,1427,1338,1364]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Heliomanes</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[151,278,1374,1400]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">subprofuga</emphasis>
Sta.
</taxonomicName>
—(
<emphasis box="[359,470,1374,1400]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Xerophila</emphasis>
)—Capri” and labelled by Bellini “ 
<taxonomicName authority=", Stabile-Capri" authorityName="Stabile-Capri" box="[850,1223,1374,1400]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="subprofuga">
<emphasis box="[850,1042,1374,1400]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Helix subprofuga</emphasis>
, Stabile—Capri
</taxonomicName>
” (MZF2—Z6969); 18 shells labelled by Bellini “ 
<taxonomicName box="[479,775,1410,1436]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="subprofuga" subGenus="Xerophila">
<emphasis box="[479,507,1411,1436]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">H.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[522,633,1410,1436]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Xerophila</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[648,775,1410,1436]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">subprofuga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, Stabile—juv.—Capri” (MCCIC—drawer 19, n. 297b). All these shells belong to the 
<taxonomicName authority="(Rossmassler, 1837)" authorityName="Rossmassler" authorityYear="1837" baseAuthorityName="Rossmassler" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[440,896,1446,1472]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hygromiidae" genus="Cernuella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="cisalpina">
<emphasis box="[440,662,1446,1472]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Cernuella cisalpina</emphasis>
(Rossmässler, 1837)
</taxonomicName>
species complex.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="360" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,1265,1725]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,1482,1508]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Remarks:</emphasis>
having been instituted on the basis of insignificant morphological characteristics, we rank it infrasubspecific, and thus not available (
<bibRefCitation author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[565,702,1518,1544]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 
<date box="[768,867,1517,1544]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" value="1945-10-02">10.2, 45</date>
.5, 45.6, glossary). 
<bibRefCitation author="Alzona, C." box="[1083,1248,1518,1544]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" pagination="1 - 433" refId="ref15337" refString="Alzona, C. (1971) Malacofauna Italica. Catalogo e bibliografia dei molluschi viventi, terrestri e d'acqua dolce. Atti della Societa Italiana di Scienze Naturali e del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Milano, 111, 1 - 433." type="journal article" year="1971">Alzona (1971)</bibRefCitation>
listed “ 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">hoemastoma</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Bellini, R." box="[217,360,1553,1580]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" pagination="149 - 194" refId="ref15792" refString="Bellini, R. (1915) I molluschi extramarini dei dintorni di Napoli. Monografia sintetica. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 2, 27, 149 - 194." type="journal article" year="1915">Bellini 1915</bibRefCitation>
” as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Stabile, 1864)" authorityName="Stabile" authorityYear="1864" baseAuthorityName="Stabile" baseAuthorityYear="1864" box="[580,1140,1554,1581]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicellidae" genus="Helicella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="subprofuga" subGenus="Cernuella">
<emphasis box="[580,683,1554,1580]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Helicella</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[702,814,1554,1580]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Cernuella</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[833,960,1554,1580]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">subprofuga</emphasis>
(Stabile, 1864)
</taxonomicName>
, now 
<taxonomicName authority="(Rossmassler, 1837)" authorityName="Rossmassler" authorityYear="1837" baseAuthorityName="Rossmassler" baseAuthorityYear="1837" class="Gastropoda" family="Hygromiidae" genus="Cernuella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="cisalpina">
<emphasis box="[1212,1437,1554,1580]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Cernuella cisalpina</emphasis>
(Rossmässler, 1837)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authority="Bellini, 1915" authorityName="Bellini" authorityYear="1915" box="[397,954,1589,1616]" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="subprofuga" variety="hoemastoma">
<emphasis box="[397,594,1590,1616]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Helix subprofuga</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[655,797,1590,1616]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">hoemastoma</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Bellini, R." box="[806,954,1589,1616]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" pagination="149 - 194" refId="ref15792" refString="Bellini, R. (1915) I molluschi extramarini dei dintorni di Napoli. Monografia sintetica. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 2, 27, 149 - 194." type="journal article" year="1915">Bellini, 1915</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
would be also preoccupied by 
<taxonomicName authority="Linnaeus, 1758" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="haemastoma">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Helix haemastoma</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Linnaeus, C." box="[260,437,1625,1652]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" refId="ref17590" refString="Linnaeus, C. (1758) Systema naturae per regna tria naturae, secundum classes, ordines, genera, species, cum characteribus, differentiis, synonymis, locis. Tomus I. Laurentii Salvii, Holmiae, 824 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 542" type="book" year="1758">Linnaeus, 1758</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Manganelli, G. &amp; Giusti, F." box="[449,765,1626,1652]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" refId="ref17747" refString="Manganelli, G. &amp; Giusti, F. (1988) Notulae malacologicae, XXXVIII. A new Hygromiidae from Italian Apennines and notes on the genus Cernuella and related taxa (Pulmonata: Helicoidea). Bollettino Malacologico, 23, 327 - 279." type="book" year="1988">Manganelli &amp; Giusti (1988)</bibRefCitation>
considered this taxon as belonging to the “small 
<emphasis box="[1324,1436,1626,1652]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">Cernuella</emphasis>
group”, with an uncertain identity. Specimens ascribed to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Rossmassler" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[823,961,1662,1688]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hygromiidae" genus="Cernuella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="cisalpina">
<emphasis box="[823,961,1662,1688]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">C. cisalpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were found again in Capri Island during recent field studies (
<bibRefCitation author="Petraccioli, A. &amp; Barattolo, F. &amp; Crovato, P. &amp; Cretella, M. &amp; Maio, N. &amp; Aprea, G." box="[377,628,1697,1724]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" pagination="19 - 48" refId="ref18257" refString="Petraccioli, A., Barattolo, F., Crovato, P., Cretella, M., Maio, N. &amp; Aprea, G. (2005) Guida pratica al riconoscimento dei macrogasteropodi terrestri attuali e fossili dell'Isola di Capri. Bollettino Sezione Campania ANISN, 29, 19 - 48." type="journal article" year="2005">
Petraccioli 
<emphasis box="[506,562,1698,1724]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="360">et al.</emphasis>
2005
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Petraccioli, A. &amp; Crovato, P. &amp; Cretella, M. &amp; Maio, N. &amp; Aprea, G. &amp; Barattolo, F." box="[639,700,1698,1725]" pageId="17" pageNumber="360" pagination="77 - 86" refId="ref18314" refString="Petraccioli, A., Crovato, P., Cretella, M., Maio, N., Aprea, G. &amp; Barattolo, F. (2006) I Gasteropodi continentali dell'Isola di Capri: risultati preliminari. In: Guglielmi, R. &amp; Nappi, A. (Eds.), La Natura in Campania: aspetti biotici e abiotici. Gruppo Attivo Campano A. R. C. A. - Onlus, Napoli, pp. 77 - 86." type="book chapter" year="2006">2006</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
